OL,3,CRMT calls for action to tackle
OL,4,C'escalating violence' on Southern
OL,5,CRailway
OL,7,FThe biggest railway workers union is
OL,8,Fcalling for action to tackle claims of
OL,9,Fescalating violence on busy train
OL,10,Froutes.
OL,12,FThe Rail, Maritime and Transport union
OL,13,F(RMT) said there had been a "serious
OL,14,Fescalation" in violent and anti social
OL,15,Fbehaviour across Southern and Gatwick
OL,16,FExpress services, operated by Govia
OL,17,FThameslink Railway (GTR).
