OL,4,C'escalating violence' on Southern
OL,5,CRailway
OL,7,FGTR said it takes the personal safety
OL,8,Fand security of everyone on its
OL,9,Fnetwork seriously and physical or
OL,10,Fverbal abuse of any kind against staff
OL,11,Fis "absolutely unacceptable".
OL,13,FRMT general secretary Eddie Dempsey
OL,14,Fsaid: "The level of violence on GTR's
OL,15,FSouthern and Gatwick Express services
OL,16,Fand stations, has reached a crisis
OL,17,Fpoint and is totally unacceptable.
OL,19,F"Our members are being assaulted,
OL,20,Fthreatened and abused at work and the
OL,21,Fcompany is not doing enough to stop it.
