OL,3,CRMT calls for action to tackle
OL,4,C'escalating violence' on Southern
OL,5,CRailway
OL,7,F"GTR must take urgent action now to
OL,8,Fprotect staff and passengers or we
OL,9,Fwill have to consider all our options,
OL,10,Fincluding industrial action.
OL,12,F"We will not tolerate a situation
OL,13,Fwhere workers are left exposed and
OL,14,Funsupported while this behaviour goes
OL,15,Funchecked."
OL,17,FThe RMT is running a campaign calling
OL,18,Ffor stronger protections for transport
OL,19,Fworkers and a zero-tolerance approach
OL,20,Fto violence and abuse across the rail
OL,21,Fnetwork.
