OL,5,CRailway
OL,7,FGovia Thameslink Railway's safety,
OL,8,Fhealth and security director Sam Facey
OL,9,Fsaid: "We take the personal safety and
OL,10,Fsecurity of everyone on our network
OL,11,Fincredibly seriously and physical or
OL,12,Fverbal abuse of any kind against our
OL,13,Fcolleagues is absolutely unacceptable.
OL,15,F"Last year we launched a #2.5 million
OL,16,FAntisocial Behaviour Improvement Plan,
OL,17,Fcreated following feedback from
OL,18,Fstakeholders including the police, and
OL,19,Fsome of our staff and trade unions
OL,20,Frepresentatives.
