OL,7,F"We remain fully committed to tackling
OL,8,Fthis issue by working closely with the
OL,9,Funions and building on what we've done
OL,10,Fso far ` this includes making more
OL,11,Fthan 1,500 body worn cameras
OL,12,Favailable, which studies show reduce
OL,13,Fassaults by 47% and also gather vital
OL,14,Fevidence to prosecute.
